      "id": "PopularPost358691",
      "post_content": "I am >SO< disappointed that nobody had mentioned the fact that this card can do something I learned called \"[Firebreathing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Firebreathing).\"  \nIn other words, you can use that +1 +0 ability anytime you want during your turn as long as you can pay for it.  \nThe amount of untapped mountains you have is the amount you can supercharge your dragon buddy!",
