    {
      "id": "PopularPost371491",
      "post_content": "While this iconic critter is nowhere as viable in Constructed today as it was in the early years of Magic, it still remains a very powerful bomb in Limited. Just yesterday, I won an M14 draft with Shivan Dragon. I delayed casting it until I felt that my opponent was out of removal, and it won me the game each time it resolved throughout the entire draft. That draft basically paid for itself thanks to this iconic red fattie.   \n  \nRemember, folks, most cards are made for Limited. If it seems worthless in a Constructed deck, it may be very powerful in Limited. ",
      "posted_by": "Joseph_Silver",
